text: Laura Sondore (born 29 December 1999) is a Latvian footballer who plays as a defender for Cypriot First Division club AEL Limassol and the Latvia women's national team. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Latvian women's footballers Category:Latvia women's international footballers Category:Torres Calcio Femminile players Category:Latvian expatriate footballers Category:Latvian expatriate sportspeople in Italy Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Italy Category:Latvian expatriate sportspeople in Cyprus Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Cyprus
